spec_data.Name: gnome-shell-extension-launch-new-instance
spec_data.Description:
This GNOME Shell extension modifies the behavior of clicking in the dash and app
launcher to always launch a new application instance.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 02 Nov 2017 02:59:27 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Always launch a new application instance for GNOME Shell
